All student notes should be written here.


How to write `Code Examples` in markdown

for JS:

```javascript
const data = "Howdy";
```

for HTML:

```html
<div>
  <p>This is text content</p>
</div>
```

for CSS:

```css
div {
  width: 100%;
}
```
